description._content: Description: Old City - Street View showing masonry window. Location: Jerusalem, Palestine Date: 1918 Description: Old City - Street View showing wooden struts across street. Location: Jerusalem, Palestine Date: 1918 Description: Old City - View from Damascus Gate towards Jaffa Gate (Note typical houses with stone roofs). Location: Jerusalem, Palestine Date: 1918 Description: Old City - Via Dolorosa (Note the flying buttreses to support old walls). Location: Jerusalem, Palestine Date: 1918 Our Catalogue Reference: Part of CO 1069/743 This image is part of the Colonial Office photographic collection held at The National Archives.
